column5: Hey All, I just got the eflyer for this retailer in Winnipeg and there are some decent deals. I ordered the Baffin Evolution Boot for $122.49 (saved $50) but did had to pay $13 for shipping. There's also an 'Eskimo 8" power auger for $329 (reg $409) and ice shelters are on sale.  Just wanted to give a 'heads up' if any one is interested. BTW, be sure to use the .ca website.  Regards, pikeslayer
I'm always dissapointed with that site.

Is that foul language or something? I went to one of their stores (in Hamburg, Pennsylvania) and it was a real palace, but good deals were hard to find. http://picasaweb.google.com/hjtoby/CabelaSOutdoorsStoreHamburgPAUSA#
Great stores/site in the States...the Canadian site...pretty much sucks.
I bought a pr of Baffin Titans from our local supplier.Got them at cost $78.
